title: The Square Root of The Diameter of the Sun in Miles
description: Despite the usual astronomic measurements being made in Metric, 930.25 miles is in fact the square root of the diameter of the sun. Enjoy this useless bit of information

title: Airspeed Velocity of The Average Unlaiden Swallow
description: To answer the question asked in Monty Python and the Holy Grail. The airspeed velocity of an unladen swallow is roughly 20.1 miles per hour.
